OL,3,CCarer from Preston made to feel like
OL,4,Ccriminal after mistake on benefit form
OL,6,FSeven years later he got a letter from
OL,7,Fthe Department for Work and Pensions,
OL,8,Fand was prosecuted for fraud.
OL,10,FHe was made to wear a tag, he was made
OL,11,Fto sell his home to pay off his debt
OL,12,Fand the toll on his mental health was,
OL,13,Fand still is, devastating.
OL,15,FTo make things worse, this year George
OL,16,Freceived a letter from the DWP - they
OL,17,Fapologised and admitted that George
OL,18,Fhad probably been telling the truth.
OL,20,FA DWP spokesperson said
