OL,6,F"We are committed to fairness in the
OL,7,Fwelfare system, with safeguards in
OL,8,Fplace for managing repayments, while
OL,9,Fprotecting the public purse.
OL,11,F"Claimants have a responsibility to
OL,12,Finform DWP of any changes in their
OL,13,Fcircumstances that could impact their
OL,14,Faward, and it is right that we recover
OL,15,Ftaxpayers' money when this has not
OL,16,Foccurred."
OL,18,FGeorge, now living in sheltered
OL,19,Faccomodation, has vowed to continue
OL,20,Fhis fight to clear his name.
